title: Building True Oneness in Marriage Part 7
itunes:author: John Fuller & Grey Smalley
itunes:summary: A healthy marriage is built by two people who are selflessly serving each other. John, Greg and Erin explain how to stop manipulating your spouse, and serve in a God-honoring way. Featuring Dr. Larry Crabb.
